--- META ---
name: TLS connection example
tags: [tls]

--- TLS ---
ca_cert: /path/to/ca.crt
client_cert: /path/to/client.crt
client_key: /path/to/client.key

--- ADDRESS ---
localhost:443

--- ENDPOINT ---
helloworld.Greeter/SayHello

--- REQUEST ---
{
  "name": "TLS World"
}

--- RESPONSE ---
{
  "message": "Hello, TLS World!"
}
